    <div class="activities-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Beyond the Classroom</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--white)">Co-Curricular Activities</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We cultivate talent, discipline, and teamwork through a rich variety of student programs and events.</p>
